title: Is Caitlyn Jenner Shopping for a Book Deal?
text:
Is Caitlyn Jenner Shopping for a Book Deal? Posted today at 3:00pm 
James White/E! Entertainment (LOS ANGELES) -- Caitlyn Jenner has already opened up about her life in a sit-down interview with ABC News and on her reality show, I Am Cait , and now she's reportedly in position to land a book deal. 
A source tells Us Weekly that publishers are seeking a book deal with the the 65-year-old, who revealed in April that she was transitioning into a woman. “They want her to do a memoir,” adds the insider. 
“Caitlyn is in a really great place right now,” a Jenner pal tells the magazine. “She’s very happy. Life is good.” 
The reality star and former Olympian already has a couple of books to her credit: 1977's Decathlon Challenge and the 1996 self-help guide Finding the Champion Within .
